ign:middle;border-collapse: collapse;border: #ccc 1px solid; "><div style="font-size:10pt; text-align:left; ; text-indent:0pt;">Four</div></td><td style="vertical-align:middle;border-collapse: collapse;border: #ccc 1px solid; "><div style="font-size:10pt; text-align:right; text-indent:0pt;">$64,100 </div></td><td style="vertical-align:middle;border-collapse: collapse;border: #ccc 1px solid; "><div style="font-size:10pt; text-align:right; text-indent:0pt;">$33,700 </div></td></tr><tr style="vertical-align:middle;border-collapse: collapse;border: #ccc 1px solid; "><td style="vertical-align:middle;border-collapse: collapse;border: #ccc 1px solid; "><div style="font-size:10pt; text-align:left; ; text-indent:0pt;">Three</div></td><td style="vertical-align:middle;border-collapse: collapse;border: #ccc 1px solid; "><div style="font-size:10pt; text-align:right; text-indent:0pt;">$59,000 </div></td><td style="vertical-align:middle;border-collapse: collapse;border: #ccc 1px solid; "><div style="font-size:10pt; text-align:right; text-indent:0pt;">$30,300 </div></td></tr><tr style="vertical-align:middle;border-collapse: collapse;border: #ccc 1px solid; "><td style="vertical-align:middle;border-collapse: collapse;border: #ccc 1px solid; "><div style="font-size:10pt; text-align:left; ; text-indent:0pt;">Two</div></td><td style="vertical-align:middle;border-collapse: collapse;border: #ccc 1px solid; "><div style="font-size:10pt; text-align:right; text-indent:0pt;">$57,600 </div></td><td style="vertical-align:middle;border-collapse: collapse;border: #ccc 1px solid; "><div style="font-size:10pt; text-align:right; text-indent:0pt;">$26,900 </div></td></tr><tr style="vertical-align:middle;border-collapse: collapse;border: #ccc 1px solid; "><td style="vertical-align:middle;border-collapse: collapse;border: #ccc 1px solid; "><div style="font-size:10pt; text-align:left; ; text-indent:0pt;"><br/> Independent</div></td><td style="vertical-align:middle;border-collapse: collapse;border: #ccc 1px solid; "><div style="font-size:10pt; text-align:right; text-indent:0pt;"><br/> </div></td><td style="vertical-align:middle;border-collapse: collapse;border: #ccc 1px solid; "><div style="font-size:10pt; text-align:right; text-indent:0pt;"> </div></td></tr><tr style="vertical-align:middle;border-collapse: collapse;border: #ccc 1px solid; "><td style="vertical-align:middle;border-collapse: collapse;border: #ccc 1px solid; "><div style="font-size:10pt; text-align:left; ; text-indent:0pt;">Single, no dependents</div></td><td style="vertical-align:middle;border-collapse: collapse;border: #ccc 1px solid; "><div style="font-size:10pt; text-align:right; text-indent:0pt;">$23,500 </div></td><td style="vertical-align:middle;border-collapse: collapse;border: #ccc 1px solid; "><div style="font-size:10pt; text-align:right; text-indent:0pt;">$23,500 </div></td></tr><tr style="vertical-align:middle;border-collapse: collapse;border: #ccc 1px solid; "><td style="vertical-align:middle;border-collapse: collapse;border: #ccc 1px solid; "><div style="font-size:10pt; text-align:left; ; text-indent:0pt;">Married</div></td><td style="vertical-align:middle;border-collapse: collapse;border: #ccc 1px solid; "><div style="font-size:10pt; text-align:right; text-indent:0pt;">$26,900 </div></td><td style="vertical-align:middle;border-collapse: collapse;border: #ccc 1px solid; "><div style="font-size:10pt; text-align:right; text-indent:0pt;">$26,900 </div></td></tr></table><div style="margin:0 0 1em 0;font-size:10pt; margin-left:0pt; text-indent:0pt;">*Applies to independent students with dependents other than a <br/>spouse.</div><table frame=""><tr><td colspan="2" valign="bottom"><div style="font-size:9pt; text-align:center; text-indent:0pt;">CAL GRANT PROGRAM ASSET CEILINGS<br/></div></td></tr></table><table frame="box" style="border-collapse: collapse;border: #ccc 1px solid; "><tr style="vertical-align:middle;border-collapse: collapse;border: #ccc 1px solid; "><td style="vertical-align:middle;border-collapse: collapse;border: #ccc 1px solid; " valign="bottom"><div style="font-size:9pt; text-align:center; text-indent:0pt;"/></td><td style="vertical-align:middle;border-collapse: collapse;border: #ccc 1px solid; " valign="bottom"><div style="font-size:9pt; text-align:center; text-indent:0pt;">Cal Grant A,<br/> C, and T</div></td><td style="vertical-align:middle;border-collapse: collapse;border: #ccc 1px solid; " valign="bottom"><div style="font-size:9pt; text-align:center; text-indent:0pt;">Cal Grant B</div></td></tr><tr style="vertical-align:middle;border-collapse: collapse;border: #ccc 1px solid; "><td style="vertical-align:middle;border-collapse: collapse;border: #ccc 1px solid; "><div style="font-size:10pt; text-align:left; ; text-indent:0pt;"><br/> Dependent**
